        <div class="more-img"><div class="img-placeholder" style="width:100%;height:100%;background:linear-gradient(145deg,#4a6b5a,#2e4a3a);"></div></div>
        <div class="more-tag">TRAVEL &middot; GUIDE</div>
        <h4>Bukchon Hanok Village: A Walking Guide</h4>
